      <section class="content">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="sec-head">
            <h2>pharmacies</h2>
            <p>
              Pharmacies are retail stores that sell medicines, pharmaceutical products,
              and other medical products to the public. 
              Pharmacies are considered important centers for healthcare in society, 
              where people can obtain the medicines, pharmaceutical products, and other health products they need to improve 
              their health and treat illnesses
            </p>
            <div class="head-shape">
              <span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
